data.description:
Welcome home! Turn key & ready for you. Perfectly located just 15 mins to downtown & minutes from Santa Fe Dr. and I-25. Discover the perfect blend of comfort & convenience in this delightful 4 bedroom, 2 bath home in Ruby Hill. Showcasing an array of features that cater to both relaxation & practicality, this home is great for you to make Colorado living in Denver. In front, you're greeted by the practicality of an RV gate & generous parking, making it ideal for those with multiple vehicles or a love for road adventures.
Inside, the home welcomes you w/a tasteful combination of neutral colors, bright light, fresh paint, & highly coveted, original wood flooring. All creating an ambiance that's welcoming, warm & elegant. The welcoming & bright living room serves as a perfect gathering space for family and friends, while the well-appointed kitchen is a dream for any culinary enthusiast. Boasting pristine white cabinetry, sleek granite counters, & SS appliances it's ready to enhance your cooking experiences. Comfort meets style in the bedrooms, w/lots of light, comfy carpet & generously sized closets for your own personal storage. Convenience is promoted on the main level w/an updated modern bathroom, adding a touch of modern classiness to your daily routines. The home continues to impress w/its basement, updated additional living space and upgraded recessed lighting! This area includes a cozy family area, two bedrooms, and an additional bathroom, perfect for guests or as a private retreat. Outside, the sizable backyard awaits your personal touch. It features an oversized shed & plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing in the tranquility of your own outdoor haven. Located just minutes away from parks, shopping centers, & more, this home is perfectly positioned to enjoy the best of the local area. Don't miss the opportunity to make this gem your own, experience its charm, & soak in Colorado living in the highly desired Ruby Hill!
